{
  "Name": "UCameraComponent",
  "Description": "Represents a camera viewpoint and settings, such as projection type, field of view, and post-process overrides.\n   The default behavior for an actor used as the camera view target is to look for an attached camera component and use its location, rotation, and settings.",
  "Variables": [
